    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "You would do something like that:\n\n``` js\n    queryHook: $.debounce(function(query, search) {\n      search(query);\n    }, 1000);\n```\n\nThanks for all the feedbacks and issues, much appreciated, really. We have a tutorial section #849 planned that would go deeper into cases like that.\n",
